1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks for handwritten text recognition, which is a common application of computer vision techniques. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper deals with text recognition, which is a subfield of natural language processing. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks, which is a common technique in machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with the use of AI techniques for text recognition. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with the recognition of text, which is a common task in information retrieval.
